profile: At Renovatio we handle all of your renovation needs - big or small.  From start to finish, we can offer innovative design ideas to help you visualize your project and have prompt, professional trades people who deliver quality finishings on time and on budget. Whether it's replacing floors, updating kitchens and bathrooms, painting or finishing basements, our teams of highly-skilled trades people can do it all!
